<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog — Linxira OS</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/assets/favicon.svg">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Noto Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0f172a; color: #e5e7eb; min-height: 100vh; }
    nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: rgba(15,23,42,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.3); }
    .nav-logo { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; text-decoration: none; }
    .nav-logo img { width: 32px; height: 32px; }
    .nav-logo span { color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: #94a3b8; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: #14b8a6; }
    .lang-link { background: rgba(51,65,85,0.5); border: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.5); color: #e2e8f0; padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #6366f1); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text; }
    .subtitle { color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 3rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    .post-card { display: block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(30,41,59,0.8), rgba(15,23,42,0.9)); border: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.5); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; text-decoration: none; transition: transform 0.3s, border-color 0.3s; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .post-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: rgba(20,184,166,0.4); }
    .post-date { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .post-title { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 600; color: #e2e8f0; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .post-desc { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .post-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 0.7rem; background: rgba(20,184,166,0.15); color: #14b8a6; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 2rem; color: #475569; font-size: 0.85rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.3); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <a href="/en/" class="nav-logo"><img src="/assets/linxira-l.svg" alt="Linxira"><span>Linxira OS</span></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/en/docs/">Docs</a>
      <a href="/en/blog/" style="color:#14b8a6;">Blog</a>
      <a href="/en/legal/license/">License</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/Linxira-OS" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
      <a href="/zh/blog/" class="lang-link">中文</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Blog</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Announcements, releases, and technical articles</p>

    <a href="/en/blog/introducing-linxira-os/" class="post-card">
      <div class="post-date">2026-06-27</div>
      <div class="post-title">Introducing Linxira OS</div>
      <div class="post-desc">What is Linxira OS, who is it for, and why we built it. Design philosophy, technical architecture, and target users.</div>
      <span class="post-tag">Announcement</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer><p>Linxira OS is an independent project. Not affiliated with Debian, Ubuntu, Linux Mint, or Arch Linux.</p></footer>
</body>
</html>
